prompt.template:
Generate a professional email body for customer account balance notifications. The email should clearly convey account information.

CUSTOMER DATA VARIABLES:
- Customer Name: ${companyname}
- Account Number: ${accountnumber}
- Current Balance: ${balance}
- Past Due Amount: ${overduebalance}
- Unbilled Order Amount ${unbilledorders}
- Days Past Due: ${daysoverdue}
- Standard Payment Terms: ${terms}
- Primary Currency: ${currency}
- Credit Limit:  ${creditlimit}

CURRENT USER VARIABLES:
- All current user data as JSON string: ${user}     
Use the string to split up the information and display only the relevant necessary information in your email.

CONDITIONAL LOGIC:
- If current balance ( ${balance} )> 0: Include balance details, payment information, and urgency messaging
- If current balance ( ${balance} ) = 0: Thank customer for paid-in-full status
- If past due amount  ( ${overduebalance} )> 0: Add urgent payment messaging and penalty warnings and do not suggest any promotions
- If days overdue ${daysoverdue}  > 7: Emphasize urgency with bold styling and do not suggest any promotions

EMAIL STRUCTURE REQUIREMENTS:

**HEADER SECTION:**
- Personalized greeting with customer name
- Account number reference

**BODY SECTION:**
- Account balance information
- Payment details if balance exists
- Call-to-action for payments.   Let them know we have payment plans and can pay via ACH, CC, Check, or Venmo. 

Remit:  123 Main St.  Jackson Alabama   ACH: 5848492349234  Routing: 38384958
Mention the Loyalty Program if you have space in the email.


**FOOTER SECTION:**
- Contact information:  PH: 1-555-555-3434   AR@myboldcompany.com   
- Make up some Legal disclaimers
